data.description: Charming 3-Bedroom, 2-Bathroom Brick Home in Loxley, Alabama  Welcome to your new home in the heart of Loxley, Alabama! Built in 2019 this beautiful, well-maintained brick home offers comfort, convenience, and a touch of Southern charm. Nestled in a friendly neighborhood, this property is perfect for families, professionals, and anyone seeking the tranquility of small-town living.  3 spacious bedrooms provide ample space for relaxation and personalization. Each room features large windows, allowing plenty of natural light to fill the space.  2 full bathrooms offer both convenience and privacy. The master bathroom includes a luxurious soaking tub and separate shower, and a double vanity creating a peaceful retreat.  The kitchen boasts modern appliances, abundant counter space, and lots of cabinet space!  The open-concept design creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The living room is open and the formal dining area offers an elegant space for special occasions.  Enjoy the Alabama weather on your back patio, perfect for grilling and outdoor gatherings. The yard is spacious, well-maintained, and fenced in providing plenty of room for gardening and play.  A two-car garage and a spacious driveway provide ample parking space for you and your guests.  Impeccably maintained brick exterior Tranquil neighborhood in Loxley Spacious bedrooms and bathrooms Inviting open-concept design Well-appointed kitchen Master suite with soaking tub and separate shower Beautiful outdoor patio with a fenced in large back yard  Loxley, Alabama, offers a charming small-town atmosphere with easy access to nearby amenities, schools, and highways, making it a convenient location for both work and play. Just minutes from the interstate making it a quick drive to Mobile, and Pensacola.  Call your favorite realtor today and schedule a showing!
